<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV73">
<l>vālveṇ ṇilavula kārac curakkumveṇ ṭiṅkaḷeṉṉum</l>
<l>pālviṇ curavi curamutir mālai paritivaṭṭam</l>
<l>pōluñ cuṭaraṭa lāḻippi rāṉpoḻi lēḻaḷikkuñ</l>
<l>cālpiṉ ṟakaimaiko lāntami yāṭṭi taḷarntatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fever-breeding evening, with the sky cow [and her] milk, called the white moon,</l>
<l>that flows forth to fill the world with pure white moonlight, [means] the declining of a solitary woman.</l>
<l>Is that the manner of excellence in which the lord with the glowing murderous discus,</l>
<l>that resembles the sun’s orb, cares for the seven groves?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
